                           61va-vb, 117ra-va, 123ra-124va.&#xD; - The word እገሌ is marked by thin
                           lines above and below on fols. e.g., 28ra, 29rb, 40va, 72va-vb,
                           73ra-rb.&#xD; - Minor notes and writing exercises: <locus target="#1v">1v</locus>, 11v, 86v, 87r, 95v.</item>
